
Ranger Help for: assess
=======================

SYNTAX:      assess <opponent>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   1
BASE SP:     2*GLEVEL+5
SKILL TYPE:  knowledge

SUMMARY:    
This allows a Ranger to assess his or her opponent up against themselves.
It will match up your ratings against your opponent's and give you some
idea of how hard it would be to kill. It also shows if your opponent
is of your enemy race or not. 'Assess' does not take into account your
primary and secondary terrains, in which in most cases you have an
advanatage over your opponents.

